name: Quiet Quarry Runway by Stephy Fung

metadata.name: Arkose by Stephy Fung
metadata.description:
As you approach the rocky terrain, you are struck by the rugged beauty of the surroundings. The rocks are a mix of warm beige and browns and they stretch out before you. The heat of the sun is tempered by the gentle shadows of the trees that line the edges of the terrain. Despite the rugged terrain, there is a sense of peace and tranquillity that permeates the landscape. You feel completely at one with nature, surrounded by the beauty and serenity of this summer landscape.

This collection was created with the feeling of tranquillity in mind. With everything the world being so chaotic and noisy; the digital garments are here to transport us to a place that is filled with beauty and serenity. As always Stephy's design encompasses the blend between traditional Chinese elements and streetwear which can be seen in this collection.
